---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import '../styles/global.css';
---

<BaseLayout title="Contact" description="Get in touch with the SaaSStatsHub team.">
  <article class="max-w-[640px] mx-auto px-6 py-12 article-body">
    <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-4">Contact</h1>
    <p>We read every email. Here's how to reach us:</p>

    <h2 id="general">General Inquiries</h2>
    <p><a href="mailto:sangaypopo@gmail.com">sangaypopo@gmail.com</a></p>

    <h2 id="press">Press &amp; Media</h2>
    <p>If you'd like to cite our data or interview the team, email <a href="mailto:sangaypopo@gmail.com">sangaypopo@gmail.com</a>. Please include your outlet and deadline.</p>

    <h2 id="corrections">Corrections</h2>
    <p>Spotted an outdated number or a sourcing issue? Email <a href="mailto:sangaypopo@gmail.com">sangaypopo@gmail.com</a> with the article URL and the specific data point. We typically respond within 48 hours.</p>

    <h2 id="partnerships">Partnerships</h2>
    <p>For sponsored content, data partnerships, or research collaboration, reach out at <a href="mailto:sangaypopo@gmail.com">sangaypopo@gmail.com</a>.</p>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
